= SDIFFSTORE _dstkey_ _key1_ _key2_ ... _keyN_ =
_Time complexity O(N) where N is the total number of elements in all the provided sets_

 This commnad works exactly like SDIFF but instead of being returned the resulting set is sotred in _dstkey_.

== Return value ==

[ReplyTypes Status code reply]
